         these zones are dead because of zones like OT or LOIO.. i would bet that over 1/2 the people just go lake/FM->OT->DL.  I think one of the reasons is that they are so far from any major city and the fact that with the ever growing item list that the items found here really arnt worth going for as lower levels because they can just buy better with the money they have.  I have one twink and I would love to do some dungeon fighting before sebilis but I cant ever find groups to go to these places.  I think verant was on the right track adding stuff like summon spells and rez spells at lower levels to encourage people to go to these places but they need to add in something that makes them more accessable or some more of a benifit to go there.. it really cant be items because then you have every high lvl farming.. maybe rings of some sort that are 1 group doable that can only be activated by certain level ranges? Maybe better xp modifiers? i dont know.  I for sure dont want to see every mid 20's to mid 40's dungeon turn into another CT with awsome items great xp but only high lvls because i feel it would help more for lower levels to start getting dungeon experience while they are lower level.</P><P>Here's to shattered dreams, lost hopes and the lies I believed of ever being someone.<BR>Xalten Deadbeat - Rodcet Nife<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=51022" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=51022</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
